Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Plugin-OSPrereqs

{{$NEXT}}

  [ADDED]

  - detect incorrect usage of plugin from a bundle, rather than allowing
    invalid code to be silently added to Makefile.PL

0.009     2018-04-21 20:36:30+02:00 Europe/Oslo

  [ADDED]

  - Makefile.PL generated code now conditionally sets prereqs into
    the list of fallback prerequisites as well.

0.008     2016-09-12 10:30:34-04:00 America/New_York

  [ADDED]

  - Can munge both Makefile.PL and Build.PL

  [PREREQS]

  - Now uses Test::Deep::JSON for json comparision tests;
    drops direct support on JSON.pm

0.007     2016-04-23 22:21:56-04:00 America/New_York

  [PREREQS]

  - Removed unused Path::Class prerequisite

0.006     2016-02-25 17:00:14-05:00 America/New_York

  [CHANGES]

  - Requires List::Util 1.33 instead of List::AllUtils

0.005     2014-07-15 17:43:22-04:00 America/New_York

  [DOCUMENTED]

  - Added DynamicPrereqs plugin to SEE ALSO

0.004     2014-07-15 17:23:19-04:00 America/New_York

  [ADDED]

